	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You call out to the poisons afflicting a creature or object, drawing them out with a few swift motions, weakening or slowing the effects of poisons that are already present, whether in a vial of poison or afflicting a creature.</em></p><p><strong>Ritual Casting Time:</strong> 1 Minute</p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><ul><li><p>All food and drink in the area is purified and rendered free of &amp;reference[poison] and &amp;reference[disease], though it may still be rotten or inedible. This has no effect on magical poisons or diseases.* This effect is permanent.</p></li><li><p>A creature currently afflicted with a poison or disease is bolstered against the effect for the next 8 hours. They have advantage on any saves against the poison or disease's effects, or any save made to determine if it gets worse or better with time.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> This spell can remove &amp;reference[poison]{poisons} or &amp;reference[disease]{diseases} from food or drink if cast at least one level higher than the level of the spell that made the poison or disease, if applicable.</p>",
